SHARE - Static variable in interface model.Actions
Static integer that is used for informing Observers of Share action that happened to the model so it can be properly handled.
share(MutableTreeNode, Observer...) - Method in interface model.Actions
This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
Purpose of method is to share the action with another parent, or create shortcut of the current action to the Another parent action.
share(MutableTreeNode, Observer...) - Method in class model.GeDocument
